      example="kb1"),ã€‚        old_doc: str = Query(ã€‚            ..., description="å¾…åˆ é™¤æ–‡ä»¶åï¼Œå·²å­˜å‚¨åœ¨çŸ¥è¯†åº“ä¸­", example="doc_name_1.pdf"ã€‚        ),ã€‚        new_doc: UploadFile                ]ã€‚            ],ã€‚        ),ã€‚):ã€‚    if (streaming):ã€‚        def generate_answer ():ã€‚            last_print_len = 0ã€‚            answer_result_stream_result =   "knowledge_base_id"]ã€‚        vs_path = get_vs_path(knowledge_base_id)ã€‚ã€‚        if not os.path.exists(vs_path):ã€‚            await websocket.send_json({"error": f"Knowledge base )ã€‚        turn += 1ã€‚ã€‚async def stream_chat_bing(websocket: WebSocket):ã€‚    """ã€‚    åŸºäºbingæœç´¢çš„æµå¼é—®ç­”ã€‚    """ã€‚    await websocket.accept()ã€‚    turn = 1ã€‚    while True:ã€‚
